title: The Demonic Statue | American Horror Stories - Episode 5: "Ba'al" (HQ Clip)
author: AHS Crave
description: The fifth episode of American Horror Stories (the official American Horror Story/AHS spin-off series), titled "Ba'al"— written by Ali Adler, Manny Coto, & directed by Sanaa Hamri— stars Billie Lourd as Liv Whitley, Ronen Rubinstein as Matt Webb, Vanessa Williams as Dr. Eleanor Berger, Misha Gonz-Cirkl as Norma, Virginia Gardner as Bernadette, Chad James Buchanan as Rory, Jake Choi as Stan, Kimberley Drummond as Emma, Michael B. Silver as Dr. Mounds, & Dane DiLiegro as the demon, Ba'al.
